<F P=100> SYRIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Israeli Knesset Member on Official Visit to Syria </TI></H3>
<H4>   Meets With President </H4>
<F P=102> JN0903175194 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1615 GMT 9 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0903175194 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At 1230 today, President Hafiz al-Asad received the 
delegation of the 1948 Palestinians led by 'Abd-al-Wahhab 
Darawshah. Members of the delegation offered their condolences 
on the loss of the nation of Staff Major Engineer Paratrooper 
Basil al-Asad. The president thanked members of the delegation 
for their noble sentiments and sincere condolences. 

</TEXT>

